headline: Why Nvidia Is Pushing Accenture Stock Higher Today
summary: Accenture (NYSE: ACN) stock is climbing higher in Tuesday's trading despite a bearish backdrop for the broader market.  Accenture is gaining ground today thanks to fresh news about its expanding partnership with Nvidia (NASDAQ: NVDA).  Accenture profiled its new software suite built on technologies from the artificial intelligence (AI) leader, and other team-ups between the two companies have been highlighted at this year's CES trade show.
